HOW TO SUPPORT KEZACO

   o If you're a commercial firm, or if you're many and have lot of money, contact me for BUYING Kezaco or
     a licence to use it.
      If you're a single user, then read the following lines.

   o send me a word once you'll have tried it (my address is in Copyrights)

   o tell me you really need it, so I'll continue rewriting most important routines

   o tell me in what purpose you use it (reading news from usenet, archiving your
     japanese CD collection (as I), or anything else...)

   o tell me what is your configuration (Amiga model/Clone, memory, processor, OS,...)
     so that I know if it works everywhere. (I wonder if people with graphic cards
     are getting a correct output)

